title: George.Clarkes.Amazing.Spaces.S05E01.480p.x264-mSD.mkv
description:
The architect extraordinaire is back for another tour of offbeat small builds, from space-saving retreats to reconditioned vehicles, at home and abroad.




George Clarke's Amazing Spaces - Series 5, Episode 1



George meets a father and son building an ambitious clifftop retreat and a young architect embarking on his first commission - a garden pavilion for his gran. Master craftsman Will Hardie sets out to transform the humble beach hut into the most unlikely of holiday getaways, and in Germany, George visits a modern house in a medieval town.




Original Air Date: 17-Sep-2015
